description: Returns a list of integrations between CloudWatch Logs and other services in this account. Currently, only one integration can be created in an account, and this integration must be with OpenSearch Service.

nested_items.name: integrationSummaries
nested_items.description: An array, where each object in the array contains information about one CloudWatch Logs integration in this account.

nested_items.name: integrationType
nested_items.description: The type of integration. Integrations with OpenSearch Service have the type OPENSEARCH.

nested_items.name: integrationStatus
nested_items.description: The current status of this integration.
